OL,6,FA decomposing rat was found beneath
OL,7,Fcooking equipment in a kitchen
OL,8,Ftakeaway following a health inspection.
OL,10,FEnvironmental health officers from
OL,11,Fmade an unannounced inspection at
OL,12,FSantinos in Front Street, Sacriston,
OL,13,Fon 7 March 2023.
OL,15,FThey also discovered the premises was
OL,16,Fdirty and in a poor state of repair,
OL,17,Fcooking equipment was not being
OL,18,Fcleaned properly, and staff had
OL,19,Freceived inadequate food hygiene
OL,20,Ftraining.
