OL,6,FMohamad Ali Ghanbarzadeh Behbahani, of
OL,7,FCravenwood Road, Reddish, Stockport,
OL,8,Fwas the owner of Santinos at the time.
OL,10,FThe 38-year-old pleaded guilty to six
OL,11,Ffood hygiene charges at Peterlee
OL,12,FMagistrates Court this week.
OL,14,FMagistrates heard that Mr Behbahani
OL,15,Fhad been running the takeaway since
OL,16,FJune 2020, but had failed to notify
OL,17,FDurham County Council, despite this
OL,18,Fbeing a legal requirement.
