OL,6,FFollowing the inspection, Mr Behbahani
OL,7,Fsigned a voluntary closure agreement
OL,8,Fto keep the premises closed until
OL,9,Fsatisfactory improvements had been
OL,10,Fmade.
OL,12,FOn returning to Santinos later that
OL,13,Fmonth, environmental health officers
OL,14,Fwere satisfied with the improvements
OL,15,FMr Behbahini had made - and the
OL,16,Fbusiness was allowed to reopen.
OL,18,FIt went on to receive a 3-star
OL,19,F'satisfactory' food hygiene rating,
OL,20,Fbut Mr Behbahani decided to close the
OL,21,Fbusiness later that year.
