OL,6,FThe court head Mr Behbahani was
OL,7,Fapologetic during interview and
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to the charges at the
OL,9,Fearliest opportunity.
OL,11,FThe business is now permanently closed.
OL,13,FMr Behbahani was ordered by the
OL,14,FMagistrates to pay #660 in fines and
OL,15,Fcosts.
