OL,6,FJoanne Waller, head of community
OL,7,Fprotection services at Durham County
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "Food hygiene laws are
OL,9,Fin place to protect the public from
OL,10,Fwhat could potentially be life
OL,11,Fthreatening illnesses.
OL,13,F"Our environmental health team
OL,14,Fsupports food businesses in County
OL,15,FDurham to improve and maintain their
OL,16,Ffood hygiene standards.
